# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ml-trading-lab — environment template
# Copy to `.env` and fill in your own values. NEVER commit a real `.env`.
# This project is EDUCATIONAL / RESEARCH ONLY and defaults to OANDA PRACTICE.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── OANDA (PRACTICE / demo only) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Create a free practice account at https://www.oanda.com and generate a
# demo API token from: Manage API Access (fxTrade Practice).
# Do NOT use a live real-money token with this research project.
OANDA_ACCOUNT_ID=your-practice-account-id
OANDA_API_TOKEN=your-practice-api-token

# Optional explicit hosts (defaults already point at the practice endpoint).
OANDA_BASE_URL=https://api-fxpractice.oanda.com
OANDA_STREAM_URL=https://stream-fxpractice.oanda.com

# Optional: override auto-detected account currency (defaults to USD).
# OANDA_ACCOUNT_CURRENCY=USD

# ── Anthropic / Claude (only needed if you enable the AI agent blocks) ─────
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# ── Optional alerting webhook (leave blank to disable) ────────────────────
# ALERT_WEBHOOK_URL=
# ALERT_WEBHOOK_TYPE=
